{"tid":369255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鳩嗚 1,000 日","createTime":"2017-08-22T07:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T07:49:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b38124187acb450bbd88ab4197f5e659c060c699","tid":369255,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20915430_1156240824477679_3705980164504843901_n.jpg?oh=0be48eff2004e6791eb89c99f5c99505&amp;oe=5A32B638\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20915430_1156240824477679_3705980164504843901_n.jpg%3Foh%3D0be48eff2004e6791eb89c99f5c99505%26oe%3D5A32B638&h=96a1a7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我要真普選！」2014年傘運過後，爭取真普選的民主鬥士陸續面對政治清算，遭律政司狂追猛打淪為階下囚。雨傘是一朵朵的花，不枯也不散。當年時任特首的梁振英，曾呼籲多到佔領區消費，一批支持民主人士，「響應」呼籲深宵到旺角等地購物，並以普通話諧音「鳩嗚」作諷刺。行動至今已經歷1,000天，一批支持民主人士仍然堅持到旺角街頭，以「鳩嗚」遊行宣示對民主和真普選的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n多名民主派人士，包括梁國雄、姚松炎、譚得志、曾健成、周偉雄、范國威、譚凱邦、曾健超、韓連山等，昨晚到「鳩嗚」熱點旺角西洋菜街舉行民主論壇。他們高舉黃傘和扣上黃絲帶，並高叫「我要真普選」等口號，強調要為下一代的自由撐下去。現場又大派燒豬和切蛋糕，紀念旺角「鳩嗚團」的1,000天。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/124853124283126/photos/a.1156239654477796.1073743050.124853124283126/1156240824477679/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F124853124283126%2Fphotos%2Fa.1156239654477796.1073743050.124853124283126%2F1156240824477679%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=X6Djyr7Uwvr%2FHWJcRpc4ZOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=11576036\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/124853124283126/photos/a.1156239654477796.1073743050.124853124283126/1156240824477679/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%B3%A9%E5%97%9A%E5%9C%98byMK-Mickey-344995145702031/?ref=br_rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E9%25B3%25A9%25E5%2597%259A%25E5%259C%2598byMK-Mickey-344995145702031%